data.description: Welcome home! Nestled in a vibrant and family-friendly neighborhood, this immaculate three year-old residence combines modern comfort with thoughtful design. Boasting three bedrooms and two baths, this home is the epitome of contemporary living. As you step inside, you're greeted by an open-concept floor plan that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The heart of the home, the kitchen, is a chef's delight with sleek countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample cabinet space. The adjoining living room provides a cozy retreat, perfect for relaxation and entertainment. The three well-appointed bedrooms provide a serene escape at the end of the day, with the primary suite featuring a private en-suite bathroom for added convenience. The two additional bedrooms are spacious and filled with natural light, creating an inviting atmosphere. Outside, the home is a covered patio extends the living space outdoors. It's an ideal spot for enjoying morning coffee or hosting gatherings with friends and family. This residence is situated in a community that offers a park and playground for recreation and socializing. The neighborhood has a friendly atmosphere.  Conveniently located near shopping centers, schools, and major transportation routes, this home combines the tranquility of suburban living with easy access to urban conveniences.
